|ALOAD 0|Load the 0th variable onto the operand stack.|this|

What is the 0th variable? It is this., the current object. When the method was called, the receiver of the message, an instance of Example, was pushed into the local variable array of the frame created for method invocation. This is always the first variable put in every instance method.

